FEM Problem Specifications
--- ------- --------------
FEM file                         = {meshfile}
Output EXODUS II file            = {resultsfile}
GUESS file                       = contin.dat
SOLN file                        = no
Write intermediate results       = no

 ---
General Specifications
 ---
Number of processors             = 1
Output Level                     = 0
Debug                            = 0
{Ifdef(continue)}
Initial Guess                    = read_exoII_file cont.exoII 
{Else}
Initial Guess                    = read_exoII_file init.exoII 
{Endif}
{Ifdef(do_biquad)}
